So todays Saturday and I have to go to the eye doctors for an exam so I can get contacts. I guess they give an hr class to show you how to put the contacts in right. So I have to go next Monday to it, so that should be interesting. Well while I was there I got a call from my dad saying I received a letter from Joe. I was soo excited to get home, but of cource the stupid SvS Vision place was taking forever to print out my recepit so I had to wait. So when I got home I started to cry while i was opening the letter it took me 10 min to read the whole thing because i was soo happy to get it but so upset at the same time. For those of you that dont know where Joe is, he is at boot camp right now @ Parris Island in, SC to become a Marine, he left on March 21 and he will be gone for 13 weeks which will be till June 17. I know your all thinking how am I dealing with my babe gone for so long. Im actually doing pretty good, im just living day by day and I know he will be home before we know it. I miss him soo much. It sucks being a part but I know this distance between us will make our love for eachother stronger. I actually spent 2 hours today writing him a 4 page letter. I had soo much to say to him because hes been gone for 2 weeks. The only communication I have with him is writing. It sucks but atleast I get to do that.

Anyways so after I was done writing him i got ready to go to Scotts new house. Its pretty cool, I cant wait for all his summer partys there gonna be a blast. It felt soo weird hanging out will my old crew but also so much fun. The boyz played Beer pong pretty much the whole nite. Ya I never realized how bad I sucked at that game until tonite. Melissa was on a roll tho she actually beat Nick and Chris's ass, it was pretty funny. So I took my new camera with me soo there should be pictures updated on here soon of cource when I figure out how to work it on the computer. Well its bed time for me because I  know this day light savings shit is gonna kick me in the ass in the morning. So Nite Yall! : *

Wow, so its been quite along time since iv updated this biotch! It seems like forever ago, Anyways well my weekend wasnt so bad after all. Tonite Mark, Megan, Lindsay, Fish and I went to Canada. On our way there Markis was driving a little crazy and Megan and I ended up getting car sick, ill tell u thats defiantly not the best feeling in the world. It took me a while to drink my first after being still sick from the car ride. We went to Patty O's for the start then we tried out Megans Rockstar boyz club I guess he goes to, I dunno that club didnt work out the way we thought it would. It would have been more fun if there were more people but hey atleast we tried it out. The Basement was defiantly a lil scary considering the fact that none of us listen to hard core music. So of cource we ended the nite at Bentlys which wasnt so bad Shaun and Dave were there and that was about it. It was pretty dead there. When we first got there though this guy was like charging right through everyone well he bumped into fish and fish wasnt so happy so he gave the guy a lil shove back well the guy thought he was soo cool that he had like 10 more buddys with him that were like 30 yrs old because thats how old he looked just to beat fish up if he tried anything,Wow kinda sad when a 30yr old cant fight someone on his own, anyways some kid that was watching what was going on tried to calm the guy down so he would go away and eventually he did. Later on in the nite i guess that kid liked Fish or something because everytime and i mean EVERYTIME that he saw fish across the bar hed be like what up man it was funny. Anyways there was this werido kid that was tryin to be cool so he takes a seat next to us in the booths and hes like staring at Megan and I and hes talking soo loud i remind you he was like screaming to his friend across the table just so we could hear what he was saying soo then all of a sudden i hear "Excuse me.. Excuse me.. HEY!.. EXCUUUSE ME" he was trying to get our attention so we were just ignoring him, it was kinda funny well he ended up just wanting to know were the strip bar was. So on our way home there were theses 2 guys walking across the street and out of no where this guy falls flat on his face, it was soo funny, it kinda reminded me of when I did that last year except i fell in the middle of the street. Well we all wanted Hungry Howies so Mark dropped Lindsay, Fish Megan and I off and while Megan and I were walking there this guy comes right to Megan face and was like Whats your name? Shes like my names Hairy and this is Dick. It was pretty funny guess you all had to be there. So that nite ended kinda weird. We went to the Duty Fruity :o ) place and then went home luckly Mark didnt drive crazy again or else id puke.

Well peeps that was my nite in Canada im sure there will be many more to come... Sweet Dreams!
